,000元。\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　　111 　年　　2 　　月　　24　　日\r\n                              書記官    林淑慧","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TCDV/111%2c%e4%ba%a1%2c19%2c20220224%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TCDV,111,亡,19,20220224,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"亡","JNO":"19","JDATE":"20220224","JTITLE":"死亡宣告"}